ts\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt seems like squad thinks it\u0027s a bad suggestion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEh, either way it\u0027s still a good suggestion.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyways, back on topic.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLower the crash tolerance of all parts to 0.0000001 m/s\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The_Arcitect","CreatedById":189349,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-13T13:44:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRemove time warp.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"catloaf","CreatedById":204108,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-14T05:11:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave destroying a probe core shut down your pc (and make internet explorer your default browser.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DunaManiac","CreatedById":176003,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T12:22:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd the sound of screaming kerbals.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-20T13:56:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n... and their phantoms in the night.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TitiKSP","CreatedById":206756,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-21T01:58:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBad mobile version.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeadJohn","CreatedById":201293,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-21T02:19:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRedesign the forums so they are mostly bright white empty space. I like feeling like I\u0027ve gone snow blind every time I tab between the dark KSP interface and maximum-brightness forums.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The_Arcitect","CreatedById":189349,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-21T12:55:25Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey should add the feature of the computer sounding like its going to take off when you launch a rocket.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt should also be a PowerPoint presentation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"planet-creations","CreatedById":162783,"CreatedDateTime":"2020-10-22T07:38:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nReplace all strings of text with \u0022aeo\u0022 and nothing else.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Max von Kerman","CreatedById":211147,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-22T05:22:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake a submarine that doubles as an aircraft and a rocket that can reach \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Low Kerbin Orbit\u0022\u003ELKO\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stormpilot","CreatedById":195836,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-24T21:20:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMake it so the only part in the game is the Kerbal X rocket all together and that\u2019s you can\u2019t import/ export ships.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-24T21:56:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEvery time you have a vehicular failure, KSP automatically posts a video of your doomed mission to the forum.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JcoolTheShipbuilder","CreatedById":204576,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-04-24T22:00:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223960239\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u002291463\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221619301366\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289014\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022adsii1970\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, adsii1970 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n